Snowcamp - Bomb/Defuse


CT's: The T's are trying to destroy your
weapondepots for preventing you to recruite. 
You have to prvent de T's for destroying it.

T's: The CT's are recruiting to eliminate you. 
You can prevent this by destroying one of there 
weapondepots. This way they can't recruit anymore
and victory will be yours.


Note: There are 2 bomb targets in the mission.
